'''[[Lietuvos krep<U+0161>inio lyga]] 2012<U+2013>2013 (LKL)''' is the 20th season of the top basketball league of [[Lithuania]].

==Competition format==
Every team except [[BC <U+017D>algiris|<U+017D>algiris]] and [[BC Lietuvos rytas|Lietuvos rytas]] will play 22 games, two against each other. This two teams, due to their participation in [[2012<U+2013>13 Euroleague|Euroleague]], will play only eleven games, all of them away.

The eight first qualified teams will join the playoffs. Quarterfinal series will be played with a best-of-three series format, semifinals with a best-of-five and the finals with a best-of-seven games format. The last qualified of the Regular Season will be relegated to the [[National Basketball League (Lithuania)|NKL]].<ref>[http://www.lkl.lt/naujienos/beko--lkl-pasitinka-jubiliejini-20-ta-sezona/ BEKO- LKL pasitinka jubiliejin<U+012F> 20-t<U+0105> sezon<U+0105>] LKL, 25 September 2012 {{lt icon}}</ref>

